Create Map Visualization 16



 Create Map Visualisation

  1. Import Map visualization from AppSource 
  2. Drag Latitude(NewChicagoDistrict) to the Latitude Field and Longitude((NewChicagoDistrict) to the Longitude Field
  3. On the format pane, Click on Viz Settings and paste pk.eyJ1IjoidGtyYWdzIiwiYSI6ImNrN2d6eTZ3MzAxOHczZXBlMDR2dGN2ZTIifQ.gIf9RZIey_l792kbYtmWMg                  in  the Access token Field and then go back to the field pane
  4. Drag CrimeRate measure(ChicagoCrimeData) to the Color,Size , Cluster Pane
  5. Drag  CommAreaTotCrime Measure(CommunityArea) and First DistName(District) to the Tool tip
  6. Click  on the format pane and make these setting: Geocoder = Off
  7. Turn Circle on: Radius = 1,Zoom scale factor = 10, diverging on, Minimum custom colour = fec0bf , Centre custom color = fd817f,Maximum custom color = ff2700,blur = 0, stroke color = whiteMin Zoom = 6
  8. Turn on Cluster: Aggregation Function = Maximum, Cluster Radius = 30, Minimum fec0bf, Maximum = ff2700,blur = 0,Stroke width = 1,Max Zoom = 6 and Legend = off
  9. Switch on Title: Text Crime Rate by District, Font Color = white,Background color = Blue
  10. Click on Viz Setting and set Map style to Traffic Dark
